posting_body: ['Schedule a Tour Today: <URL>', 'Discover a life of ease at Palmetto Promenade.', 'At our luxury apartments in Boca Raton, residents will find a selection of one bedroom, two bedroom, and three bedroom homes that are sure to suit any lifestyle.', 'In each home, residents will enjoy the chef-caliber kitchens with quartz countertops and stainless steel appliances, private balconies, and spacious closets with built-in shelving.', 'Throughout the community at our Boca apartments, residents can take advantage of the resort-style swimming pool with private cabanas, cutting-edge fitness center, and the outdoor entertainment area.', 'Amenities:', '-Cutting edge fitness studio with cardio, strength training, Fitness On Demand and yoga studio', '-Signature two and three bedroom townhome floor plans with 2-car garages and penthouse level residences available', '-Wood flooring throughout the kitchen, living and dining areas', '-Ceiling fans included', '-Whirlpool appliance package including French door with bottom freezer in stainless steel refrigerator', '-Modern one, two and three bedroom residences', '-Dacora rocker switches and USB outlets in the living room and bedrooms', '-Resort-style swimming pool and sundeck with waterfall features', "-Spacious 9' ceilings", '-Wi-Fi access throughout residential amenities', '-11,000 SF of ground level retail with valet parking', '-Professional concierge services available', 'Call:', 'show contact info', 'Equal Housing Opportunity', 'Pricing and availability are subject to change.']
